<template>
  <button @click="logout">Logout</button>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  methods: {
    logout() {
      if (localStorage.getItem("token") != "") {
        this.$router.push({ name: "apiLogin", query: { logout: null } });
        localStorage.setItem("token" == "");
      }
    },
  },
};
</script>
